Name: Luno Amber
Description: Due to the rarity of Luno made from rare metals, some merchants began trading with polished amber, which gradually came to be known as Luno Amber. Although it is not recognized by official trading centers, Luno Amber is still indispensable for adventurers, providing significant help during growth and adventures.
